     fhir:div [ fhir:v "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Narratif généré : EnsembleValeurs jdv-absent-or-unknown-devices-cisis</b></p><a name=\"jdv-absent-or-unknown-devices-cisis\"> </a><a name=\"hcjdv-absent-or-unknown-devices-cisis\"> </a><div style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: #d9e0e7; padding: 6px; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid #8da1b4; border-radius: 5px; line-height: 60%\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">version : 9; Dernière mise à jour : 2026-04-20 16:57:32+0200</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">Profil: <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/shareablevalueset.html\">Shareable ValueSet</a></p></div><ul><li>Include ce(s) code(s) tel qu'il(s) est (sont) défini(s) dans <a href=\"http://tx.hl7europe.eu/r4\"><code>http://hl7.org/fhir/uv/ips/CodeSystem/absent-unknown-uv-ips</code></a><span style=\"opacity: 0.5\" title=\"La version n'est pas explicitement indiquée. Lors de la génération de cette spécification, la version la plus récente 1.1.0 a été utilisée\"> version ⏿1.1.0</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Affichage</b></td><td><b>Définition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://tx.hl7europe.eu/r4/ValueSet/absent-unknown-uv-ips#absent-unknown-uv-ips-no-device-info\">no-device-info</a></td><td>Pas d'information sur les dispositifs médicaux</td><td>There is no information available regarding implanted or external devices for the subject.</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://tx.hl7europe.eu/r4/ValueSet/absent-unknown-uv-ips#absent-unknown-uv-ips-no-known-devices\">no-known-devices</a></td><td>Pas de dispositif médical connu</td><td>There are no devices known to be implanted in or used by the subject that have to be reported in this record. This can mean either that there are none known, or that those known are not relevant for the purpose of this record.</td></tr></table></li></ul></div>"^^rdf:XMLLiteral ]
